title: Misinformation and "The Movement": Comparisons to Buddhism, Fascism and Worse.
description:
If you're interested in seeing the article alluded to around the seven minute mark, it's titled, "The Opposite of Buddhism" (and it's written in very plain English, as it was presented to a Cambodian audience); the particular (salacious) material alluded to is (mostly) in §8:
